					.container
						.row
							.col-md-10.col-lg-7
								h1(data-caption-animate='fadeInUp' data-caption-delay='100') #1 Choice for Your Banking Needs
								p.lead(data-caption-animate='fadeInUp' data-caption-delay='250') Our Orange Card is the best option if you are looking for high-quality and reliable banking services.
								a.button.button-lg.button-primary.button-icon.button-icon-left(href='#' data-caption-animate='fadeInUp' data-caption-delay='450')
