				.swiper-slide-caption
					.container
						.row
							.col-md-10.col-lg-7
								h1(data-caption-animate='fadeInUp' data-caption-delay='100') The Brightest Card in Your Wallet
								p.lead(data-caption-animate='fadeInUp' data-caption-delay='250') Dot Bank Standard Card offers extensive list of features and benefits for corporate and individual clients.
